originalText.text: This is the best networking group/meeting I've ever attended!  Dynamic and successful individuals from all different professions all deeply committed to helping each other and their businesses in a professional, energetic, and family environment.  Truly inspirational.

originalText.text: Joining this group a year ago was one of the easiest decisions I've ever made.  This group of professionals have given me great advice on how to grow my business to the next level as well as introduce me to many new clients.  Anyone looking to join the best marketing group in NYC shouldn't just take my word for it, they should come visit and see for themselves.

originalText.text: I attend the BNI meeting here weekly, and it's great! It's helped me make a lot of new business connections that has lead to thousands of dollars in closed business for myself and my firm.
